description: Something strange has moved into the caves under Thornhill.  Navigate a maze of tunnels and caves without falling into a pit or being eaten by the monster.  Find and shoot the monster to save the town of Thornhill!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Caves Under Thornhill to start a game.
Shoot an arrow into cave three.
name: Caves Under Thornhill
shortDescription: Caves Under Thornhill is a classic maze and monster game.
